{"tid":544630,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【DSE】2018報考人數跌破6萬　創歷屆新低","createTime":"2018-01-29T16:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T18:58:29.000Z","uid":732,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"71890185cddb424440d227e33707a6cc47ed5f0c","tid":544630,"uid":732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:52:24.000Z","msg":"考評局今日公布2018年香港中學文憑試（DSE）各科考生人數。今年報考DSE總人數共有59,039名，是2012年改制後連續第6年下跌，亦是DSE報考人數最低一次。<br />\n<br />\n據考評局數據所示，報考DSE總人數共有59,039名，當中學校考生有51,675名，自修生有7,364名。在甲類選修科目方面，最多人報考的兩個選修科為生物和經濟，報考人數有14,585名及14,443名，而最少兩者則為綜合科學和音樂，報考人數僅108名及228名。<br />\n<br />\n另外首屆文憑試起，報考數學科兩個延伸部分（M1、M2）的人數和比例一直下跌，而今年報考M1、M2總人數有8,150名，較去年的8171名輕微下跌。"},{"pid":"971c3d9ae5552a628269677ab13eb03711bd533b","tid":544630,"uid":12866,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:53:07.000Z","msg":"唔係有龍年效應咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9af4e37899400cd49af8f36388b747eca202064","tid":544630,"uid":44073,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:54:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"14cbc3c057699ff0ec8890e632b7a8075e89d586","tid":544630,"uid":44073,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:54:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6f904f5b6a31e710071ea783d3df6f634dc4e6a2","tid":544630,"uid":167841,"like":5,"dislike":19,"score":-14,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:54:50.000Z","msg":"2018dse揮手區<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0141bfa199f2d9d423748dff4056fbbce74848c1","tid":544630,"uid":91115,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T16:55:13.000Z","msg":"幾年前已經predict左<br />\nnot news"},{"pid":"1e57891c2d46736280f45a0fc5ba8a31670ac482","tid":544630,"uid":33347,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-29T17:03:14.000Z","msg":"正常<br />\n2001 至 2003 好似係出生率最低既幾年"},{"pid":"9926f9b8f3b5b68749e037988a62c34422b63458","tid":544630,"uid":140309,"like